title: Shell Point Charity Golf Tournament
text:
Shell Point Charity Golf Tournament Where 
7:00 a.m. Friday, Nov. 13, 2015 Categories 
Events, Fundraisers, Sports Shell Point’s 12th Annual Shell Point Open Golf Tournament, hosted by The Legacy Foundation, offers 18 holes of golf plus cart, continental breakfast, barbecue lunch with ABC-7’s Krista Fogelsong, silent auction and raffle prizes, and the opportunity to win big hole-in-one prizes – all for a $128 fee. Proceeds benefit Memory Care at Shell Point. Hurry, space is limited! Call (239) 466-8484 today. $128.00
